    <section id="pagecontent">
        <h1> About Us </h1>
        <p>
            A family run campground ensuring the best visitor experience for
            all the campers. We are proud of our location right on  the sandy beach
            at sandy point. You can view the beautiful town of Salmon Arm right across
            the lake shadowed under Mount Ida or admire the magnificent Mount Bastion
            from the sandy point end. We happily accommodate families on various types
            of camping spots ranging from tenting (in open and trees both) to full hook
            up trailer spots. We appreciate and prefer bookings to be made over the phone
            (+1 250-832-3793). Along with the friendly atmosphere at the campground, we
            would be grateful of you to follow the campground rules and regulations.
            Thanks. Al and Doris Ono
        </p>
    </section>

